divs: Sighting DetailsI have no idea as to what possesed me to take a picture of the sky like I did but I discovered this (and other) photos while downloading them from our cameraphone. I can't think of why I would have stopped, pointed the camera up to the sky like I apparently did. This was around my house (Highland, CA) just before noon I believe and from what it appears I must have thought I saw something and took the pic then forgot about it or something I don't know. I discovered more photos as well showing the same object in multiple frames. Again I don't recall the incident at all. But these are my photos from a cameraphone I own and from my neighborhood.
Summary: Caught on film (unknown reason why I took photo of sky)
